---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Stripe from "./Stripe.astro";
import Skyline from "../assets/logo.png";
import GolfBanner from "../assets/golfbanner.png";
import Tees from "../assets/tees.png";
import Admiral from "../assets/5star.png";
import Commander from "../assets/commander.png";
import Raffle from "../assets/raffle.png";
import Cash from "../assets/cash.png";
---

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white">
  <!-- Top nautical stripe -->
  <Stripe />

  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="px-5 pt-10 pb-5 bg-white">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-2 md:gap-4">
      <h1 class="font-brush text-4xl md:text-6xl font-normal">Swing and Sip</h1>
      <span
        class="font-impact text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-gold tracking-wider"
        style="text-shadow: 3px 3px 0px #D68910;">REGATTA</span
      >
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <div class="px-8 md:px-16 py-10 bg-white leading-relaxed">
    <p class="font-bold text-lg mt-5 mb-4">Dear Community Partner,</p>

    <p class="mb-5">
      We are thrilled to announce the return of our most anticipated
      gathering — The Skyline Women's Golf Fiesta Member Guest Invitational set
      for March 24-25, 2026. This year, our signature "Swing & Sip Regatta"
      theme promises even more fun, community spirit, and business visibility
      than ever before. Join us as a sponsor and connect directly with an
      audience that loves to celebrate and support local businesses like yours.
      Our enthusiastic members and guests consistently look for ways to
      reciprocate the generosity they see at our events—making this an
      extraordinary opportunity to showcase your brand, build relationships, and
      drive business in 2026.
    </p>

    <div class="font-bold my-8 text-lg">
      Ways to Make a Splash as a Sponsor
    </div>

    <!-- Tee Sponsorship Section -->
    <div class="my-8">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-2 p-5 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg flex items-start gap-4">
        <Image src={Tees} alt="Tee sponsorship" class="w-12 h-12 shrink-0 object-contain" />
        <div>
          <div class="block mb-2 text-lg font-bold text-navy-blue">Tee Sponsorship</div>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-700">
            Put your business front and center on the course, reaching every golfer:
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Indented sponsorship options with visual cards -->
      <div class="space-y-4 max-w-2xl mx-2 mt-4">
        <!-- Admiral's 5-Star -->
        <div class="ml-6 md:ml-12 p-5 bg-gradient-to-r from-gold/10 to-transparent border-l-4 border-gold rounded-r-lg flex items-start gap-4">
          <Image src={Admiral} alt="Tee sponsorship" class="w-12 h-12 shrink-0 object-contain" />
          <div>
            <strong class="block mb-2 text-gold-dark text-lg">
              Admiral's 5-Star Sponsorship ($500)
            </strong>
            <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-700">
              Enjoy exclusive prime placement as one of only five sponsors with a solo
              banner at a signature PAR 3 hole. Your company's name and logo shine on
              the course, in our event program, and at the lively Cocktail Party on
              March 24th.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Commander's -->
        <div class="ml-6 md:ml-12 p-5 bg-gradient-to-r from-navy-blue/10 to-transparent border-l-4 border-navy-blue rounded-r-lg flex items-start gap-4">
          <Image src={Commander} alt="Tee sponsorship" class="w-12 h-12 shrink-0 object-contain" />
          <div>
            <strong class="block mb-2 text-navy-blue text-lg">
              Commander's Sponsorship ($250)
            </strong>
            <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-700">
              Make a strong impression with a branded sign at a tee box and your
              business featured in the event program.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Other Sponsorship Options -->
    <div class="my-8 space-y-4 max-w-2xl mx-2">
      <div class="p-5 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg flex items-start gap-4">
        <Image src={Raffle} alt="Tee sponsorship" class="w-12 h-12 shrink-0 object-contain" />
        <div>
          <strong class="block mb-2 text-lg">Raffle Donation</strong>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-700">
            Donate gift certificates or products for our always-popular final event
            raffle. Guests love to discover new businesses through these exciting
            prizes!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="p-5 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg flex items-start gap-4">
        <Image src={Cash} alt="Tee sponsorship" class="w-12 h-12 shrink-0 object-contain" />
        <div>
          <strong class="block mb-2 text-lg">Cash Donation</strong>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-700">
            Make a meaningful impact by contributing to help cover the event's
            costs. Complete flexibility—your support at any level fuels our
            celebration and your business recognition.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    

    <div class="font-bold  my-8 text-lg">
      Let's Celebrate Local, Together
    </div>

    <p class=" mb-5">
      Every sponsorship helps us create a vibrant, memorable event while giving
      your business outstanding exposure. Checks can be made to "SWGA Fiesta"
      mailed to Skyline Fiesta, Attn: Martha Blohm, 6098 N. Indian Trail,
      Tucson, AZ 85750 or, if you'd like the convenience, we're happy to arrange
      for pick-up at your business.
    </p>

    <p class=" mb-5">
      Join us in making the 2026 Swing & Sip Regatta our best yet—for our
      golfers, our community, and your business. Please reach out anytime with
      questions or ideas—we love tailoring sponsorship experiences that work for
      you. Thank you, in advance, for your partnership and for helping us make a
      difference in Tucson.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Contact Info -->
  <div class="px-8 md:px-16 py-10 bg-white leading-relaxed">
    <div class="mb-8">
      <p class="font-bold text-lg mb-6">With gratitude,</p>
      <p class="font-bold">Martha Blohm</p>
      <p>2026 Committee Chair</p>
      <p>
        <a href="tel:520-548-9645" class="text-amber-500 hover:text-blue-500 hover:underline transition">
          520-548-9645
        </a>
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href="mailto:swgafiesta@gmail.com?subject=SWGA%202026%20Regatta" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-amber-400 hover:underline transition">swgafiesta@gmail.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Golf course -->
  <div class="pb-20">
    <!-- Golf Course Illustration -->
    <div class="relative w-full h-48 md:h-72 mx-auto rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
      <Image
        src={GolfBanner}
        alt="Golf course background image"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />

      <!-- SKYLINE LOGO IMAGE - Centered at bottom -->
      <div class="absolute bottom-6 md:bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 z-50">
        <Image
          src={Skyline}
          alt="Skyline Country Club logo"
          class="w-32 md:w-72 h-auto"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
